t it was supposed to after the Iran strike. Is the spike temporary or a new era for the safe-haven trade?\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/gold-just-passed-its-stress-test-what-happens-next-will-tell-investors-if-theyre-right-35de6d2f\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772487600, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Iran conflict unlikely to hurt U.S. economy or boost inflation — but the Fed won’t be quick to cut rates\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580272, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"The U.S. attack on Iran won’t boost U.S. inflation or harm the economy in a major way, analysts say, unless in the unlikely case that the conflict drags on for months and sharply raises the price of oil.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/iran-conflict-unlikely-to-hurt-u-s-economy-or-boost-inflation-but-the-fed-wont-be-quick-to-cut-rates-6e7d315a\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772487180, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Trump’s war on Iran could make many things more expensive, despite his affordability promises\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580273, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"How do you campaign on “affordability” if you just pushed up prices?\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/trumps-war-on-iran-could-make-many-things-more-expensive-despite-his-affordability-promises-66060ea4\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772484180, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Iran conflict hits a market that’s more overvalued than during the 1973 oil shock\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580262, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Arab–Israeli war in 1973 and the oil embargo that followed shows that stocks don’t always rebound quickly.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/iran-conflict-hits-a-market-thats-more-overvalued-than-during-the-1973-oil-shock-f9035d9d\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772481480, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Here is the ‘worst-case scenario’ for oil and the Strait of Hormuz\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580256, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Oil climbed to its highest price since June on Monday, as conflict in the Middle East brings with it an inherent risk to the world’s available crude supplies.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/here-is-the-worst-case-scenario-for-oil-and-the-strait-of-hormuz-d1aada30\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772480400, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Why CrowdStrike’s stock just got an upgrade ahead of earnings\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580251, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"An analyst sees minimal risk to the company’s guidance and thinks shares have been overly punished by a broad selloff in the software sector.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/why-crowdstrikes-stock-just-got-an-upgrade-ahead-of-earnings-1a7450be\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772480195, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"We're upgrading our rating on Nvidia shares. Here's why\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580261, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108248994-1767729949197-gettyimages-2254367461-AFP_89UC72B.jpeg?v=1772476350&w=1920&h=1080\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\