 still do not have a permanent place to live—more than a year after they lost their Pacific Palisades property in the California wildfires.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/former-reality-tv-stars-heidi-montag-and-spencer-pratt-say-they-are-still-displaced-by-wildfires-2a7a98fd\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772532060, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"‘No toilets’? Civil trial over renovation work plays out in L.A. over Kanye West’s stripped Malibu beach house\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580375, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"A worker is seeking more than $1 million in damages from Kanye West over the renovation work of a Malibu home and has made some bizarre allegations.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/no-toilets-civil-trial-over-renovation-work-plays-out-in-l-a-over-kanye-wests-stripped-malibu-beach-house-b7d885a6\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772529720, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Gold can be called many things — just don’t say it’s an inflation hedge\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580360, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Gold’s been on a sensational run, but the one thing it can’t be described as is an inflation hedge.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/gold-can-be-called-many-things-just-dont-say-its-an-inflation-hedge-468ef2b2\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772529540, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"World’s hottest stock market suddenly blows cold with a 7% tumble\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580361, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"Mark